snippet.title: Yuppie Psycho - Welcome to Sintracorp
snippet.description:
Available April 25 on PC-Mac-Linux, on Steam and Utomik
Wishlist us: https://store.steampowered.com/app/597760/Yuppie_Psycho/

Join Brian Pasternack on his first day at one of the world’s largest companies, Sintracorp. Uncertain, unprepared, and massively unqualified, will Pasternack have what it takes to shine in Sintracorp’s hierarchy? It all depends on how he performs on his first assignment… and whether he survives it.

Do you like the music? Buy the full Soundtrack from Michael Garoad (composer of VA-11 Hall-A) here: https://garoad.bandcamp.com/album/yuppie-psycho-original-soundtrack

Join the Discord: https://discord.gg/ai 
Follow on Twitter: https://twitter.com/baroquedecay 
Like our Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/yuppiepsycho
